[ veloute ]
   1   :   1   :      15
butter : flour : chicken stock
- add butter to pan and melt
- heat on low and incorporate until wet sand
- take roux off stove
- heat chicken stock
- gradually incorporate stock into roux

[ sauce supreme ]
- veloute
- double cream
- good hit of lemon juice

[ mustard ]
- sauce supreme
- salt
- dijon mustard
- wholegrain mustard
- combine on low heat
- add chopped tarragon and mix through

[ sace ivoire ]
- heavy cream
- salt
- tomato puree
- lemon juice

[ herb veloute ]
- veloute on high heat
- basil
- dill
- parsley
- tarragon
- a splash of cream
- lemon juice
- blend

[ albufera ]
- veloute
- heavy cream
- reduced beef stock
- touch of sherry vinegar
- black pepper
